==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Betterness
<hw>Bet"ter*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality of
being better or superior; superiority.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Sir P. Sidney.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The difference by which fine gold or silver exceeds
in fineness the standard.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>better-off</ent>⟦br⟧
